body:
### Welcome to DjNRO Pages.

![DjNRO](https://code.grnet.gr/attachments/2265/logo.png)

DjNRO project scope is to provide a one-stop point for eduroam users plus an administrative platform for local eduroam admins.

DjNRO is an open-source project. You can get it via github or via the [GRNET's DjNRO repository](https://code.grnet.gr/projects/djnro/)
